visual-awr
==========

visualize Oracle AWR performance metrics using this fine grained charting tool.  Right now this is a private Git repository.  If you would like access, please contact me through github.

More information on VisualAWR, including a download of the latest release can be found at: [http://visualawr.blogspot.com/](http://visualawr.blogspot.com/)
